# Large Paper Swatches (TPG Sheets), Pantone Color of the Year 2024

## Large-format color for Fashion, Home + Interiors (FHI) applications

Sku#: 13-1023TPG

$ 17.50

Add To Cart

Large-scale sheets allow product designers and brand owners to wrap products in Pantone Color of the Year 2024: PANTONE® 13-1023 Peach Fuzz is a velvety gentle peach whose all-embracing spirit enriches mind, body, and soul. Ideal for realistic color representation and verification, Pantone’s TPG (Textile Paper-Green) format Sheets can also be chipped for communication and specification of staple colors.

- Designed for visualizing and manipulating color on product in three dimensions
- Can be cut to create large-scale palettes for viewing at a distance
- One Pantone FHI Color per 8.5” x 11” sheet
- Printed gridlines on the back for creating up to 80 1” x 1” chips

All Swatch Cards are non-returnable/non-refundable.

